<section xml:id="sec-Rates-Ratio-Proportions-and-Percents" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
    <title>Rates Ratio Proportions and Percents</title>

    <introduction>
        <p>
            Rates, ratios, proportions, and percents are all ways of comparing quantities. 
            They are used in many different situations, from cooking to sports to finance. 
            Understanding how to work with rates, ratios, proportions, and percents is an important part of being able to solve problems in many different areas.
        </p>
